Stakeholder analysis:

In this case, we only focus on Primary Stakeholders & Secondary Stakeholders

Primary Stakeholders
Patient, Children, Elderly

The Pain Point:
1 Forget to take Medicine / Supplement
2 Don’t know how to take Medicine / Supplement correctly because its complexity
3 Users need to have a healthy routine on having Medicine / Supplement

Goal:
1 Remind them to have Medicine / Supplement on time
2 Show usage history
3 Easy to create and edit a personal plan


Secondary Stakeholders
Doctor, Caregiver
The Pain Point:
1 They can not pay all attention on the care recipient
2 Sometimes they can not help care recipient in reality

Goal:
1 Ensure care recipients are following their plan
2 Receive notifications if doses are missed
3 Help to track their body health
